big surprise.

11:13.800 --> 11:15.097
I'm a very bad liar,
babe.

11:15.150 --> 11:16.538
Gina is not going to
ruin your career

11:16.580 --> 11:17.923
because my father
broke up with her.

11:19.280 --> 11:20.714
Your father broke up
with Gina?

11:20.760 --> 11:22.580
I should go away.

11:24.550 --> 11:25.847
Oh, Lizzie, I feel awful.

11:25.900 --> 11:27.720
I'm gonna call Gina.No, no, no.

11:27.770 --> 11:29.374
I think you might
want to give her a minute.

11:29.420 --> 11:31.240
Or longer.

11:31.290 --> 11:32.633
Hey, listen,

11:32.690 --> 11:34.294
Stella, Aiden and I
were thinking that

11:34.340 --> 11:35.944
we should do family dinner
at the bar tomorrow night.

11:35.990 --> 11:38.300
You know, with everything
that's happened,

11:38.340 --> 11:40.513
it might be nice for all of us
to be together.

11:40.560 --> 11:42.904
I think that
is so sweet, dear.

11:42.960 --> 11:44.086
I'd love to.

11:44.130 --> 11:45.529
I have to admit,

11:45.570 --> 11:47.390
I'm sorry to hear
that Gina won't be there.

11:47.440 --> 11:49.784
She really
made your father happy.

11:49.830 --> 11:51.616
And she made my eyes happy.

11:51.660 --> 11:53.617
Mama couldn't touch,
but she could look.

11:55.930 --> 11:57.318
Stella: Oh, hey.

11:57.360 --> 11:59.180
Thanks for grabbing those
for the party.

11:59.240 --> 12:00.628
I would've been here sooner,

12:00.670 --> 12:02.923
but I just got accosted
at Ophelia's Flowers.

12:02.980 --> 12:05.540
A woman wanted to help me
take these to your grave.

12:05.590 --> 12:08.503
I'm guessing
she saw the video.

12:08.550 --> 12:09.585
Wow.

12:09.640 --> 12:11.290
Well,
we'll just take it down.

12:11.330 --> 12:13.503
I don't know how much good
that's gonna do.

12:13.550 --> 12:15.769
It's already been reposted
a bunch of times.

12:15.820 --> 12:17.686
Then we'll make
another one.

12:21.210 --> 12:22.427
I think you're going
a little bit overboard

12:22.480 --> 12:23.902
with the lighting.

12:23.960 --> 12:27.737
I just want everyone to see
how healthy I am

12:27.790 --> 12:28.780
and how happy we are.

12:28.830 --> 12:30.218
Okay.

12:34.050 --> 12:35.302
You ready?

12:35.360 --> 12:36.395
Yeah.

12:40.360 --> 12:42.829
Okay. We are live.

12:42.890 --> 12:45.791
Hi, my name is
Stella Jane Abbott,

12:45.850 --> 12:48.194
and I do not want you
to marry my husband.

12:48.240 --> 12:50.413
Turns out
I'm not drying after all.

12:50.460 --> 12:53.714
And we are going to live
happily ever after.

12:54.730 --> 12:56.118
Hmm.

12:56.160 --> 12:57.468
<i>Didn't realize
you could comment in real time.</i>

12:57.510 --> 12:58.636
This is fun.

12:59.990 --> 13:01.116
Wait, what?

13:01.170 --> 13:02.729
W-Why would he be
freaking out?

13:02.780 --> 13:04.168
Oh, no,
I'm not freaking out.

13:04.210 --> 13:06.816
I am really very excited
about our future together.

13:07.960 --> 13:10.952
What does our future
look like?

13:11.000 --> 13:13.913
Well...

13:13.960 --> 13:17.487
Uh, we are setting down roots
here in Asheville.

13:17.530 --> 13:19.578
We will buy a house
someday.

13:19.620 --> 13:22.487
Uh, we'll start a family...

13:22.540 --> 13:24.349
Listening to Wes
tell the world

13:24.410 --> 13:26.538
exactly what he wanted
our future to be

13:26.580 --> 13:29.663
made me realize
I had no idea what I wanted.

13:31.370 --> 13:33.156
Is that what I want?

13:33.200 --> 13:36.249
I guess living in the --
in the house I grew up in,

13:36.290 --> 13:37.849
in the town I grew up in,

13:37.900 --> 13:42.201
a-and running the hospital
that I basically grew up in...

13:42.250 --> 13:43.638
seems kinda small

13:43.690 --> 13:45.727
considering there's
a whole world out there.

13:45.780 --> 13:48.078
But it could be great,
who knows?

13:48.130 --> 13:50.428
The point is,
we are great today

13:50.480 --> 13:51.641
<i>and we are
figuring out tomorrow</i>

13:51.700 --> 13:52.644
'cause I'm not dead.

13:52.700 --> 13:53.690
So...bye.

13:55.050 --> 13:57.473
Thanks a lot.What did I do?

13:57.530 --> 13:59.259
You just told the whole world
what our future looks like

13:59.310 --> 14:00.835
and put me on the spot
to agree with you,

14:00.880 --> 14:02.302
which makes it seem like
we're not on solid ground,

14:02.360 --> 14:03.441
which was
the whole point.

14:03.490 --> 14:04.616
All I did was pitch

14:04.660 --> 14:06.139
a pretty harmless future
for us,

14:06.190 --> 14:08.010
and you
totally freaked out.

14:08.060 --> 14:10.017
I did not freak out.
